A man was left critically injured after being stabbed by his friend after an alleged argument.On arrival paramedics found the man seated on the pavement on Cranbourne Avenue in Benoni CBD.Paramedics assessed the man and found that he had sustained several stab wounds and was in a critical condition.The man was treated for his injuries and transported under advanced life supervision to Themba Memorial Hospital for further care.Local authorities are investigating the case further.-TNA Reporter 